{"tid":1633651,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"大家必須知道口罩嘅重要性","createTime":"2019-10-07T04:46:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T05:12:23.000Z","uid":260434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"58cbcba15400dfd332a68799895e25051c36bf84","tid":1633651,"uid":260434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:46:29.000Z","msg":"大家知唔知道口罩嘅重要性啊<br />\n<br />\n香港嘅空氣污染已經無以復加，上年三個人已經死喺空氣污染相關嘅疾病上（<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80%E5%B0%88%E9%A1%8C/207722/%E7%A9%BA%E6%B0%A3%E6%AE%BA%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%BA3-%E7%A9%BA%E6%B0%A3%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%86%A011%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%87%B6%E7%90%86\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E5%258D%2580%25E5%25B0%2588%25E9%25A1%258C%2F207722%2F%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E6%25AE%25BA%25E6%25AD%25BB%25E4%25BA%25BA3-%25E7%25A9%25BA%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E6%25B1%25A1%25E6%259F%2593%25E7%2596%25BE%25E7%2597%2585-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E5%2586%25A011%25E5%259F%258E%25E5%25B8%2582-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E6%2587%25B6%25E7%2590%2586&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4sLrQrhaJullgCUoYOUuTa8%3D&h=4d5dcc42\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E5%8D%80%E5%B0%88%E9%A1%8C/207722/%E7%A9%BA%E6%B0%A3%E6%AE%BA%E6%AD%BB%E4%BA%BA3-%E7%A9%BA%E6%B0%A3%E6%B1%A1%E6%9F%93%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E5%86%A011%E5%9F%8E%E5%B8%82-%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E6%87%B6%E7%90%86</a><br />\n<br />\n以前香港人經常戴口罩，但最近唔知道點解少左，甚至直接唔出街.<br />\n<br />\n咁唔得啊，必須提醒返大家戴口罩係為左大家嘅健康<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">屌唔撚兜圈啦</span></span><br />\n<br />\n講真啊，反蒙面法其實真係唔係針對勇武，而係和理非. 好多和理非真喺驚左啊. 我身邊唔少和理非真喺唔咁行出來. 咁落去勇武會比大家孤立，情況會越來約危險<br />\n<br />\n所以promote<span style=\"color: red;\">全民口罩</span>刻不容緩<br />\n<br />\n原因如下：<br />\n1. 令政府知道，就算如何打壓香港市民，我地都係唔會怕<br />\n2. 製造國際輿論<br />\n3. 令和理非對口罩常規化，抵銷對蒙臉法嘅恐懼，唔會因為蒙臉法而之後唔再出來抗爭<br />\n4. 講抗爭繼續帶入社區<br />\n5. 越多人戴口罩就越難執法<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n建議大家除左連農牆貼文宣，每日都到各區交通交匯點排放口罩😷. 講全民口罩嘅訊息帶比市民<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">唔好再停留喺連登同溫層啊. 宜家好多文宣真喺脫離群眾啊</span><br />\n<br />\n我今日就買幾箱口罩，聽日去巴士站同黨鐵站口派，我一個人實孤力弱. 有無人願意幫我啊？ 你都好似我咁落街派口罩，鼓勵大家注意健康就得嘅啦.<br />\n我真喺好擔心大家比空氣污染傷及健康啊<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港時代革命<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n對唔住P牌仔出post，認同就幫忙推啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9454ed2ee22b84762545741a63a40db23e3f8ce4","tid":1633651,"uid":110832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:48:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c1d32e624276814e7ae0fbaa5fcd92779a2f698","tid":1633651,"uid":307619,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T04:49:08.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: green;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果和理非連咁小野都做唔到<br />\n就唔好學人話抗爭</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rHxjrJf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrHxjrJf.jpg&h=8688cd40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">聽日<span style=\"color: red;\">全民三罷</span>！！！<br />\n當十幾歲嘅學生中槍，<br />\n咁多個人冇咗隻眼，<br />\n咁多個義士死諫，<br />\n仲可以正常返工返學？</span>"},{"pid":"590de6ae2d381603edf0d9048d6c217bc84ece33","tid":1633651,"uid":89767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T05:12:23.000Z","msg":"日日戴口罩<br />\n抗爭日常化<br />\n<br />\n我戴咗口罩出街啦，你呢？"}]}